{"title":"桥工之歌","authors":["扬子浪"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"建桥工人多奇志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四处　扬子浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日出东海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花向太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥梁工人心向党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想来武装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄关险道任飞渡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万水千山无阻挡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山长河插红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上当闯将。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶满天霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踩万顷浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲风雷收眼底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海云水涌胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年饮马黄河畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日挥戈扬子江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥梁工人走天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五湖四海是家乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江心擂战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里风雷响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扒杆如林旗如海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器轰鸣凯歌壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水晶宫前筑墩柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云深处架桥梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建桥工人多奇志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢教山河换新装。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}